                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-123-off660 t18320705-123-crimeloc662"></join>, and lodge at my grand-mother's. The prisoner lodged in the same room; I do not know what he is - I left my shirt and money in the room, at half-past nine o'clock at night on the 7th of May; when I awoke the next morning I missed my shirt; and the money was taken from my fob, which had been cut off.</p>
               <p>
            
