            . I slept in the same room; I left my coat in the room when I went to bed at night, about half-past ten or eleven o'clock; when I got up in the morning it was missed - I did not see the prisoner, and have not found the coat.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320705-123-person1104">
                  GEORGE 
                  COLLIER
